The social bonds were issued on attractive terms, reflecting the strong interest among investors. This is a vote of confidence in the EU as issuer and borrower. 🇪🇺

The entire EU SURE bond of up to €100 billion will be issued as social bonds.

We have issued a €17 billion inaugural social bond under the EU SURE instrument.

By raising money on the market, we can help protect jobs & keep people in work.

This is a first step towards entering the major league in global debt capital markets.
